* Rework how Connection objects point to addons and addon configs.
* Fix throttling (so we don't get booted from freenode when joining over 9000 channels upon connect.
* Allow for addons to provide additional attributes and methods for Connection, Channel, User, and Server objects.
* Rewrite a parser factory factory, move rfc1459, rfc2812, ircv3, and ircd-specific support into separate modules.
